    title: "How to Choose a Web Agency: 15-Point Checklist",
    excerpt: "What to look for — and what to avoid — when hiring a web agency for your business site or e-commerce project. Portfolio, contracts, communication, post-launch support, and red flags explained.",
    category: "Бізнес та зростання",
    tags: ["Agency", "Web Development", "Business", "Hiring"],
    date: "2026-04-12",
