      "Email automation is one of the highest-ROI activities in digital marketing. The average email automation sequence returns $38 for every $1 spent — but most businesses either do not use automation at all or set it up once and never optimize it.",
      "The 5 automation sequences every business needs: Welcome sequence (triggered on signup). Onboarding sequence (triggered on first purchase or sign-up completion). Abandoned cart or abandoned form sequence. Re-engagement sequence (for subscribers who have not opened in 90+ days). Post-purchase or post-service follow-up.",
