      "Lead magnet quality matters more than quantity: A specific, immediately usable tool outperforms a generic ebook. Examples that work well: a calculator or template relevant to your industry, a curated resource list, a short video training on a specific problem, a quiz with personalized results, an exclusive dataset or benchmark report.",
