      "Content upgrades — the highest-converting lead magnets: A content upgrade is a bonus resource inside a blog post that is directly related to what the reader is already reading. If you have a post about Facebook Ads, offer a free Facebook Ads targeting checklist. Content upgrade conversion rates are typically 5-30% versus 1-3% for sidebar sign-up forms.",
      "Exit intent pop-ups still work — when done right: Show pop-ups at exit intent (when the cursor moves toward the browser tab), not on arrival. Offer something genuinely valuable for their specific context. A/B test the headline. Exit intent pop-ups with relevant offers convert at 3-7%.",
