    title: "Website Security Hardening: The 20-Point Checklist for 2025",
    excerpt: "Most website hacks exploit the same 5-10 issues. Here is the security hardening checklist that addresses the most common vulnerabilities — practical steps, not theory.",
    category: "Безпека",
