    title: "Cloud Server vs VPS in 2025: Which One Is Right for Your Site",
    excerpt: "The line between cloud and VPS has blurred. Here is a clear comparison of what each means today, the real performance differences, and which setup makes sense for what workload.",
    category: "Хостинг та інфраструктура",
    tags: ["Hosting", "Cloud", "VPS", "Infrastructure"],
    date: "2026-05-09",
    readTime: 8,
