    title: "Legal Essentials for Digital Businesses: What You Actually Need in 2025",
    excerpt: "Terms of service, privacy policies, contracts, IP protection — the legal documents every digital business needs, why they matter, and what to watch out for.",
    category: "Право та GDPR",
    tags: ["Legal", "Business", "Privacy Policy", "Terms of Service"],
    date: "2026-05-10",
    readTime: 10,
    author: "Alex Kovalenko",
